title: Between Worlds (2018 Thriller) Nicolas Cage’s Haunted Trucker Meets Psychic Nightmare

sources.title: Between Worlds (2018 Thriller) Nicolas Cage’s Haunted Trucker Meets Psychic Nightmare
sources.description:
A young woman in a coma appears to be possessed by the soul of a tormented man's dead wife.

Original title: Between Worlds (2018) 

Director: Maria Pulera
Writers: Maria Pulera

Main cast:
Nicolas Cage - Joe
Franka Potente - Julie
Penelope Mitchell - Billie
Garrett Clayton - Mike
Lydia Hearst - Mary

Genres: Supernatural thriller, Drama, Fantasy, Mystery
Release date: December 21, 2018
Filming location: Mobile, Alabama
